** {{Flag|California}} – [[波莫納學院|波莫納學院]]：{{tsl|en|Doctor of Humane Letters|人文文学博士}}<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.pomona.edu/news/2014/02/04-princess-maha-chakri-sirindhorn-thailand-receives-honorary-degree-pomona-college |title = Princess Maha Chakri Sirindhorn of Thailand Receives Honorary Degree From Pomona College |work = Pomona College in Claremont, California – Pomona College |access-date = February 23, 2016 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160314163816/https://www.pomona.edu/news/2014/02/04-princess-maha-chakri-sirindhorn-thailand-receives-honorary-degree-pomona-college |archive-date = March 14, 2016 |url-status = dead }}</ref>
** {{Flag|Indiana}} – {{tsl|en|Indiana University Bloomington|印第安納大學伯明頓分校}}：{{tsl|en|Doctor of Humane Letters|人文文学博士}}<ref>{{cite web |url = http://newsinfo.iu.edu/news/page/normal/16611.html |title = IU to present honorary degrees to Thai princess and surgeon general of the Navy |publisher = IU News Room: Indiana University|access-date = February 23, 2016}}</ref>
** {{Flag|Illinois}} – [[北伊利诺伊大学|北伊利诺伊大学]]：{{tsl|en|Doctor of Humane Letters|人文文学博士}}<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.nationmultimedia.com/national/HRH-Princess-Sirindhorn-gets-royal-NIU-welcome-30215283.html |title = HRH Princess Sirindhorn gets royal NIU welcome |date = September 19, 2013 |work = The Nation |access-date = February 23, 2016}}</ref>
** {{Flag|Maryland}} – [[约翰斯·霍普金斯大学|约翰斯·霍普金斯大学]]：{{tsl|en|Doctor of Humane Letters|人文文学博士}}<ref name=JHUhonorary>{{cite web |title = JHU Honorary Degrees Awarded |url = http://web.jhu.edu/commencement/honorees/alpha.html |access-date = April 7, 2011}}</ref>
** {{Flag|Massachusetts}} – {{tsl|en|Bay Path University|贝佩丝大学}}：{{tsl|en|Doctor of Humane Letters|人文文学博士}}<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.masslive.com/news/index.ssf/2011/05/bay_path_college_graduates_tol.html |title = Bay Path College graduates told to accept change |work = masslive.com |access-date = February 23, 2016}}</ref>

